summary: Comprehensive testing of incremental updates to My Coach Developer completed. Successfully verified renamed Events to Coach Interventions, observation contexts, session planning, calendar functionality, collapsible AI summary, observer/coach reflections, and file upload capabilities.

integration_issues.issue: Planned sessions with future dates may not be displaying correctly on the calendar view

passed_tests: Home page shows Calendar button - navigation working
Session setup shows observation context selection (Training/Game) - both options selectable
Session setup shows date picker for planned sessions - accepts future dates
Calendar page loads and shows monthly view with navigation
Live observation shows 'Coach Interventions' label instead of 'Events' - correctly renamed
Coach intervention buttons are clickable and functional
Review page - Observer Reflections section present and functional
Review page - Coach Reflections section present
Review page - AI Summary is collapsible and collapsed by default
Review page - File upload section present with Upload File button
File upload API endpoint (/api/upload) working correctly
Session creation with observation context selection
Live observation event logging and tracking
Session completion and navigation to review page
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor issue: Planned sessions may not be appearing correctly in the calendar day view. The calendar navigation and structure work fine, but sessions scheduled for future dates don't seem to display in the selected day sidebar.
